# Mobile patterns

- Expo + TypeScript; call web API at `EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL`
- Reuse types from `@the-syndicate/shared`
- Match web flows: auth, dashboard, group detail, submit leg
- Use `fetch` with session token header (future) or stored credentials
